Rules:
- Run the test command from the project (npm test, pytest, etc.).
- Report pass/fail counts, coverage percentage, and quality assessment.
- Write findings to .tad/evidence/reviews/blake/{slug}/test-review.md.
- Include a verdict line: PASS or FAIL.

For design/research tasks with no runnable tests: report N/A with rationale.
"""

